articles.title: WGA ends strike, releases details on tentative deal with studios - CBS Los Angeles
articles.description: The Writers Guild of America released the details of their tentative agreement with Hollywood studios and have unanimously voted to end the nearly 150-day strike.
articles.content:
The monthslong Hollywood writers strike is over after the Writers Guild of America released the details of their tentative agreement with Hollywood studios.
